<plot>A young Welsh teenager, Owain Haggar, finds a can of film in the shed at the bottom of the garden. It turns out to be the long-lost picture "The Maid of Cefn Ydfa" made by his ancestor, William Haggar, who was a travelling showman and pioneering film-maker at the turn of the twentieth century.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?252369</url></doc>
